spec_data.Name: intltool
spec_data.Description:
This tool automatically extracts translatable strings from oaf, glade,
bonobo ui, nautilus theme, .desktop, and other data files and puts
them in the po files.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 08 Aug 2017 10:19:58 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Utility for internationalizing various kinds of data files
